  h2 Projects - 15 min
  ol
    li What is the relationship between the root of the file system and the username root?
    li Why shouldn't users always be the root user?
    li How do you list out the contents of a protected folder e.g. /root?
    li How do you stop your elevated privileges when you are done with them?
    li How can you re-run a command you just ran with sudo?

  h2 Nice Job!
  p You now know the basics of using sudo!
